{"tid":998052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本計劃幫中國蓋廁所　教中國人上廁所","createTime":"2019-01-27T15:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T04:36:55.000Z","uid":47714,"like":810,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbaa1ddb8cab9867e94ad6008f164cfdeb34035","tid":998052,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180417/1335854/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180417%2F1335854%2F&d=RFvMBDugZ9Q5DE7FF%2B10mzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=70cbec96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180417%2F1335854%2F&h=e261d106\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180417/1335854/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tiny.cc/f6pq2y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2Ff6pq2y&h=b3da8f43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年是日本與中國《和平友好條約》簽署40周年，日本政府為改善兩國關係，決定支援中國政府推動「廁所革命」，透過衞生教育和技術，幫中國蓋廁所，並教導中國人使用廁所，不要隨地大小便。<br />\n <br />\n《日本經濟新聞》周六（14日）報導，日本政府希望通過這項「廁所外交」，為改善日、中兩國關係，創造契機。日本外務省、經濟產業省、環境省，將就相關支援計劃，啟動討論。日本政府已向TOTO等日本企業進行諮詢，日本駐中國大使館也已與中國政府開展協商。為把握中國農村的需求和實際情況，日本近期將派出考察團，到實地調查、研究。<br />\n <br />\n報導指，中國的公共廁所中，有很多是無法沖洗的旱廁、蹲坑廁所，農村地區有些廁所甚至沒有門或間隔設置。日本期望支援中國在農村普及廁所技術，及進行相關的衞生教育，教導當地人用廁所。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nトイレ革命で日中友好　技術や衛生教育で日本が支援<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nikkei.com%2Farticle%2FDGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000%2F&d=RFvMBDugZ9Q5DE7FF%2B10mzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6c4ee41f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000/</a>"},{"pid":"cbb903845cb75a96acff3d201f14dff6bd1bc23c","tid":998052,"uid":6111,"like":963,"dislike":3,"score":960,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"好似教狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"