.com/article/DGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000/</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？？狗都要教去廁所啦 何況畜牲  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe241b8508d41d452808e19a59aaf554dd20227f","tid":998052,"uid":1643,"like":257,"dislike":3,"score":254,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"嘥氣，支那人係唔受教，仲覺得你厚多士"},{"pid":"167cf45fc3136cce12ef73e1ce50b2f0852f7736","tid":998052,"uid":125193,"like":94,"dislike":1,"score":93,"quote":{"pid":"cbb903845cb75a96acff3d201f14dff6bd1bc23c","tid":998052,"uid":6111,"like":963,"dislike":3,"score":960,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"好似教狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？？狗都要教去廁所啦 何況畜牲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c24d6a62e025b33c8faa8f3bb10ade00a5dd54","tid":998052,"uid":78429,"like":172,"dislike":2,"score":170,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:02:02.000Z","msg":"下一步應該裝晶片先定絕育先"},{"pid":"c5bbfd81cbdcde84dde9c80775e67dc3d82a4e56","tid":998052,"uid":224561,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"quote":{"pid":"58c24d6a62e025b33c8faa8f3bb10ade00a5dd54","tid":998052,"uid":78429,"like":172,"dislike":2,"score":170,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:02:02.000Z","msg":"下一步應該裝晶片先定絕育先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"大規模撲殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bce8abc8f419a982b3033a755832053b7033e87","tid":998052,"uid":171313,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"教完班強國人等佢哋去日本唔好周街屙"},{"pid":"26fb8178e3584376696b01b025d891d4c1a08124","tid":998052,"uid":78429,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c5