ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T22:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dbzDvsaUZM4/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FdbzDvsaUZM4%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=62b3b84b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6eb377146fc06b1ecd20ac7b49959d7970b3e8c","tid":998052,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16d439ba9344bdf40612c1dd2235bb67343d810b","tid":998052,"uid":125193,"like":234,"dislike":1,"score":233,"quote":{"pid":"ddbaa1ddb8cab9867e94ad6008f164cfdeb34035","tid":998052,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180417/1335854/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180417%2F1335854%2F&d=RFvMBDugZ9Q5DE7FF%2B10mzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=70cbec96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180417%2F1335854%2F&h=e261d106\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180417/1335854/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tiny.cc/f6pq2y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2Ff6pq2y&h=b3da8f43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年是日本與中國《和平友好條約》簽署40周年，日本政府為改善兩國關係，決定支援中國政府推動「廁所革命」，透過衞生教育和技術，幫中國蓋廁所，並教導中國人使用廁所，不要隨地大小便。<br />\n <br />\n《日本經濟新聞》周六（14日）報導，日本政府希望通過這項「廁所外交」，為改善日、中兩國關係，創造契機。日本外務省、經濟產業省、環境省，將就相關支援計劃，啟動討論。日本政府已向TOTO等日本企業進行諮詢，日本駐中國大使館也已與中國政府開展協商。為把握中國農村的需求和實際情況，日本近期將派出考察團，到實地調查、研究。<br />\n <br />\n報導指，中國的公共廁所中，有很多是無法沖洗的旱廁、蹲坑廁所，農村地區有些廁所甚至沒有門或間隔設置。日本期望支援中國在農村普及廁所技術，及進行相關的衞生教育，教導當地人用廁所。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nトイレ革命で日中友好　技術や衛生教育で日本が支援<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nikkei.com%2Farticle%2FDGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000%2F&d=RFvMBDugZ9Q5DE7FF%2B10mzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6c4ee41f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000/</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？？狗都要教去廁所啦 何況畜牲  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:00:37.000Z","msg":"最怕教撚完佢 反咬你一口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790b068f4a607bdd1d15f9e1ec6a76ca8a5fccb4","tid":998052,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:02:00.000Z","msg":"日本人真係好高尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d130b8773a6ab8aa1b5a78649cc9b509fd2b9e6e","tid":998052,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:13:06.000Z","msg":"支那狗唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406341c1f59446c39ebc86de0f1aa7fdcad7e541","tid":998052,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:16:00.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為日本人入埋廁所幫佢地冚廁所蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c43f11022a1d41b8209fdfe79ce802c9aa71cd9","tid":998052,"uid":161341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:24:32.000Z","msg":"支那狗都教得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但習種玩緊文革，點教"},{"pid":"0b9677831e5905e48998a8fe09a610d6986afafd","tid":998052,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:28:48.000Z","msg":"咁耐都未有屎圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab7dfddb2bbbd279e59d869633332c8e53d2543","tid":998052,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:30:07.000Z","msg":"辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb25434ee8b770d5ac9576127a99bf66f596fd81","tid":998052,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"灜國又蠃"},{"pid":"e3a4c9a9a93b1cc2e406c2e461358bcec1034208","tid":998052,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1618f66716187585f3aa2c28a9a786eaeaabb972","tid":998052,"uid":58167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:38:08.000Z","msg":"Old news黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcb2c62c3a2a2571c2137c2b225745d056e01cb","tid":998052,"uid":141261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:48:51.000Z","msg":"佢地會拆左個屎坑 攞去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26851f269fba773f8c41c9f04b72af535df24b84","tid":998052,"uid":13739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cbb903845cb75a96acff3d201f14dff6bd1bc23c","tid":998052,"uid":6111,"like":963,"dislike":3,"score":960,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"好似教狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:51:17.000Z","msg":"直頭係"},{"pid":"3796c4015e65868b73b5476610ca3b1d18a98418","tid":998052,"uid":25240,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e3a4c9a9a93b1cc2e406c2e461358bcec1034208","tid":998052,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:00:58.000Z","msg":"d 支那狗而家無恥到講埋咩「日本有小禮而無大義」黎打飛機<br />\n周街瀨屎瀨尿然後話自己「知大義」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係沒有最無恥 只有更無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dec274e96badadf46cb9aa48777080587422672","tid":998052,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbb903845cb75a96acff3d201f14dff6bd1bc23c","tid":998052,"uid":6111,"like":963,"dislike":3,"score":960,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"好似教狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:01:20.000Z","msg":"點解仲再咁危險去教班生番"},{"pid":"f7a087f4603e9e2b4d64cec7e740d7e820ef84aa","tid":998052,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:13:36.000Z","msg":"自主研發"},{"pid":"c6713524728b40ac1186c27d974e46a06e344723","tid":998052,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:24:17.000Z","msg":"尋日見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平，前年拍板推動的「廁所革命」，遭遇重大挫折。央視節目《焦點訪談》報導，甘肅武威、山東臨沭等地，旱廁（俗稱茅廁、茅坑）改造成沖水式廁所後，卻因設備質量、環境因素等問題，村民無法適應，最後竟改回使用旱廁。這種「花了錢，費了勁」改造的廁所閒置無用，被民眾批為「新的形式主義，為完成任務而完成任務」。<br />\n <br />\n香港《蘋果日報》報導，由於設備品質、環境因素等問題，甘肅武威市涼州區，改造的新廁所使用率很低，此外，農村因無法接入排污管網，化糞池需定期清理，僱專業車輛清運糞使的費用，成為當地村民的負擔。面對各種問題，不少鄉村的村民又重新用起旱廁。<br />\n <br />\n村民沒能從「廁所革命」中獲得實惠，央視也沒檢討習近平的政策是否有錯誤，反過來批評幹部：「明顯是有人『好事卻沒有辦好』」。<br />\n <br />\n央視報導指說，武威和平鎮改廁過程中，進行過招標，據得標的企業表示，得標價格是1套1400元人民幣（約台幣6379元），但從公司提供的內部合約來看，真實成交價格遠低於此，1套不到600元人民幣（約台幣2734元），中間的800多元（約台幣3645元）差價用在何處，仍有待相關機構調查。報導說，這種「花了錢，費了勁」改造的廁所閒置無用，被民眾批為「新的形式主義，為完成任務而完成任務」。<br />\n <br />\n針對央視的報導，甘肅省委書記林鐸表示，「辦好事為什麼總辦不好」值得武威市涼州區及該省各地區各部門深思，並強調「要加大對形式主義、官僚主義作風整治力度」。<br />\n <br />\n甘肅省長唐仁健則指出，「廁所革命」是「習近平總書記時時牽掛、親自推動，事關群眾生活品質的事」，卻被部分地方搞成「既不中看、也不中用的『閒擺設』」，「花了錢，買了民怨」。他強調，對於那些膽敢在民生項目中撈油水、積民怨的人，也要「革他們的命」。"},{"pid":"7d8f43a28a96adcfc8156e2488bf644db3998076","tid":998052,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:01:29.000Z","msg":"就算日本仔用靚料<br />\n起到個廁所靚一靚都無用<br />\n佢哋一日就幫你拆返晒出嚟攞去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ebef6f48e78262a1229cb38d5184469105c672","tid":998052,"uid":52595,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f507a7f8f4c366cb514778c0432fd726ed39785","tid":998052,"uid":98223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c3333a5f9ff0aa663ca81aeed6229555173f55","tid":998052,"uid":58931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"屌你 <br />\n<br />\n真係德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e940a9f04336a5eedf0ec292e3f7197b7b97292c","tid":998052,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905a23a609a1515d010f962f0c57320674aa4ed7","tid":998052,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"教完有幾多人會跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3877da31506b7ab4cd7fcdeb1bf5c24febaaacd5","tid":998052,"uid":32221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"咁撚侮辱既政策如果真係實行到<br />\n今代支那真係遺臭萬年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0bcf8376f8bac512e665fea57a877416482ecf","tid":998052,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:02:44.000Z","msg":"教狗咁教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog