年前好撚多<br />\n就算去行山肚痛都未至用唔到<br />\n十幾廿年前果啲我真係寧願搵個凹位就地解放"},{"pid":"69da851ae81df74fd43766c2be9006ef6f2ab779","tid":998052,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">並教導中國人使用廁所，不要隨地大小便。</span>"},{"pid":"c2dcca268f7f2f19ea4be24cbe3bc9cbe0f825b5","tid":998052,"uid":90697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16d439ba9344bdf40612c1dd2235bb67343d810b","tid":998052,"uid":125193,"like":234,"dislike":1,"score":233,"quote":{"pid":"ddbaa1ddb8cab9867e94ad6008f164cfdeb34035","tid":998052,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180417/1335854/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180417%2F1335854%2F&d=RFvMBDugZ9Q5DE7FF%2B10mzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=70cbec96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180417%2F1335854%2F&h=e261d106\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180417/1335854/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tiny.cc/f6pq2y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2Ff6pq2y&h=b3da8f43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年是日本與中國《和平友好條約》簽署40周年，日本政府為改善兩國關係，決定支援中國政府推動「廁所革命」，透過衞生教育和技術，幫中國蓋廁所，並教導中國人使用廁所，不要隨地大小便。<br />\n <br />\n《日本經濟新聞》周六（14日）報導，日本政府希望通過這項「廁所外交」，為改善日、中兩國關係，創造契機。日本外務省、經濟產業省、環境省，將就相關支援計劃，啟動討論。日本政府已向TOTO等日本企業進行諮詢，日本駐中國大使館也已與中國政府開展協商。為把握中國農村的需求和實際情況，日本近期將派出考察團，到實地調查、研究。<br />\n <br />\n報導指，中國的公共廁所中，有很多是無法沖洗的旱廁、蹲坑廁所，農村地區有些廁所甚至沒有門或間隔設置。日本期望支援中國在農村普及廁所技術，及進行相關的衞生教育，教導當地人用廁所。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nトイレ革命で日中友好　技術や衛生教育で日本が支援<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nikkei.com%2Farticle%2FDGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000%2F&d=RFvMBDugZ9Q5DE7FF%2B10mzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6c4ee41f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXMZO29401760U8A410C1MM0000/</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？？狗都要教去廁所啦 何況畜牲  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca916624962d57563d16b83e090e69fb863089d","tid":998052,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"多謝日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  華達屎華 里康賤的士!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b09fcb7308c8b7469f39fba66211f3f141845f1","tid":998052,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa14b4f6670b46b103dbd340e6137e0ae4e32d11","tid":998052,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eefe48070617b09c2b46f65a22d985a1719cc4d","tid":998052,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:54:15.000Z","msg":"變相教埋香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"香港其實整體已經好過十幾廿年前好撚多<br />\n就算去行山肚痛都未至用唔到<br />\n十幾廿年前果啲我真係寧願搵個凹位就地解放"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:25:39.000Z","msg":"我講緊香港人去廁所嘅質素，唔喺廁所硬件。<br />\n講硬件大陸都好左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb863561f7b5831b25f75254eb57dc9a0860108","tid":998052,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"大陸人冇資格講 &quot;我識自己去廁所架&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fd17a1ab1549a701632594c54c131